  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch eezeheſle fewim\nPreesterus par teem Augstu-\nneem/ un Johdeem/ un Teſteem/\nko wiꞥſch bij darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pehz teem nahze arri-\nDsan no wiſſahin Israëta Ziltim/\nkas ſawu Sirdi nodewuſchi to\nKUNGU to Israëka Deewu\nmekleht us Jeruſalemi / tam\nKUNGAM ſawu Tehwu Dee-\nwam uppureht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta eespehzinaja tee to\nWalſtibu Juhda/ un apſtipri-\nnaja Rekabeannu Salamana\nDehlu trihs Gaddus/ jo trihs\nGaddus staigaja tee eekſch Dah-\nwida un Salamana Zeſteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Rekabeams nehme\npahri pahr Maëlatu Jerimota\nDahwida Dehla Meitu/ Abiä-\nilu Elijava/Isaja Dehla Meitu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta dſemdeja tam tchohs\nDehlas/ Jeïfu/ Semariju un\nSaamn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pehz nehme wiꞥſch\nMaëku Absaloma Meitu / ta\ndſemdeja tam Abiju/ un Ataju/\nun Stsu/ un Selomitu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Rekabeains mihleja\nMaëku Absalonia Meitu wat-\nrak/ ne ka wiſſas ſawas See-\nwas un leekas Seewas / jo\nwiꞥſch bij aſtonpadefmits See-\nwas nehmis/ un feſchdefinitis\nleekas Seewas/ un dſemdiua.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Rekabeams erz\nAbiju Maëkas Dehlu par W\nneeku un Leelu-Kungu starpt\nna Brahteem/ jo wiſſch feſchki\nto par Kehnizu darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſch turrejahs g\nri/ un iſdallija no wiſſeim\nweem Debleem starp wiſſa\nJuhda un Benjamina Walsti\nwiſſds ſtiprös Pilsfahtöe /\ndeve teem Barribas papillain,\nwiſſch eekahroja dands Seei\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "ja dwidefinits un astonus D\nlus/ un feſchdefinitis Meitas.\n"
    }
  ],
